rows.label: fev08_140_130_msg0001
rows.name:
I think we've rested long
enough. Time to get moving.

rows.label: fev08_140_130_msg0002
rows.name:
We're getting closer to the
World Tree bit by bit.

rows.label: fev08_140_130_msg0003
rows.name:
Hana hope Masterpon and friends
also going to World Tree...

rows.label: fev08_140_130_msg0004
rows.name: We can only hope they are.

rows.label: fev08_140_130_msg0005
rows.name:
If we don't meet them on the
way, we should wait for them
at the base of the World Tree.

rows.label: fev08_140_130_msg0006
rows.name: Yes, that would be the best approach.

rows.label: fev08_140_130_msg0007
rows.name: What's wrong? Are we going or not?

rows.label: fev08_140_130_msg0009
rows.name:
Honestly... He's barely recovered
and already giving orders.

rows.label: fev08_140_130_msg0010
rows.name:
It appears we'll need to pass
through that cave ahead.
